    (
        '013e253b-7209-4a0a-980c-5395919ece34',
        'Trauma dumping - vilka problem ser du i din scoutkår?',
        'Trauma dumping - what challenges do you have in your local scout group?',
        'Speeddate med ett ovanligt tema: vad är det som inte riktigt fungerar i din kår? Det där som alltid gnager lite i bakhuvudet men som ingen pratar om?
I snabba rundor får du lufta problemen du ser, höra vad andra kämpar med – och kanske inse att du inte är ensam om dem. Tre minuter per person. Inga filter.',
        'What are the things that don’t quite work? The issues that keep bothering you in the background, but that no one ever brings up?

In a series of quick conversations, you’ll get the chance to share the challenges you notice, hear what others are dealing with, and maybe realise that you’re not the only one facing them. And along the way, you might meet someone with an idea that could help make things better.

Three minutes per person. No filters.',
